projects.name: Car Listing
projects.description: This is a mobile application that lists various cars on the screen. Details included are rating, pros/cons, MSRP, etc. The app also includes options for sorting and filtering.

projects.name: Cat Platformer
projects.description: This is a basic platforming game, using a cat as a player. Accumulate points by collecting fish, and battle the evil rat enemy. Development in progress.

projects.name: Chore Chart
projects.description: This is a mobile app for logging chores and rewards for a household. The app uses the google firestore database for storing people, chores, and rewards.

projects.name: Basic Drawing
projects.description: This is a basic drawing mobile application. You can draw in different thicknesses, shapes, and colors. The app also allows for undo and redo of lines drawn.

projects.name: Garden Plot Planner
projects.description: A console application garden plot planner in C#. You can choose the size of your garden plot, add/remove plants, and load plants from a file.
